oji\" /><br />\n衰衰地 GM 都 degree 職系<br />\nACO CA 只係中四五<br />\n<br />\n我指入行比起其他專業門檻低<br />\nPGDE 你肯俾錢去讀<br />\n讀完就有教師資格<br />\n有資格唔等於有教席<br />\n市面上大把 PGDE 甚至 master <br />\n就算 TA 0.幾 CM GM 照狗衝<br />\n供過於求就係咁啦<br />\n要怪就怪政府一直無視依個問題"},{"pid":"4a65a1ff70e2d0d91aa326da5e4bba94be138fad","tid":1979182,"uid":298477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"09b7e568ec62b652cf2c37cae63d3ca01df092bc","tid":1979182,"uid":304916,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d24c8f275140df385665d9a625f5a161d46ab83d","tid":1979182,"uid":298477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4719f33a38b31ea8d604f53345bf7e699139e733","tid":1979182,"uid":304916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:17:34.000Z","msg":"門檻低 GM perm 位唔夠咪咁囉<br />\nPS 前 EDB AEO, 一早轉左行"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"你拎教師同 ACO CA 比，係咪搞笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰衰地 GM 都 degree 職系<br />\nACO CA 只係中四五<br />\n<br />\n我指入行比起其他專業門檻低<br />\nPGDE 你肯俾錢去讀<br />\n讀完就有教師資格<br />\n有資格唔等於有教席<br />\n市面上大把 PGDE 甚至 master <br />\n就算 TA 0.幾 CM GM 照狗衝<br />\n供過於求就係咁啦<br />\n要怪就怪政府一直無視依個問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb16e8628e534014b523a4f3c75eaac4ff49183","tid":1979182,"uid":304916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a65a1ff70e2d0d91aa326da5e4bba94be138fad","tid":1979182,"uid":298477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"09b7e568ec62b652cf2c37cae63d3ca01df092bc","tid":1979182,"uid":304916,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d24c8f275140df385665d9a625f5a161d46ab83d","tid":1979182,"uid":298477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"你拎教師同 ACO CA 比，係咪搞笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰衰地 GM 都 degree 職系<br />\nACO CA 只係中四五<br />\n<br />\n我指入行比起其他專業門檻低<br />\nPGDE 你肯俾錢去讀<br />\n讀完就有教師資格<br />\n有資格唔等於有教席<br />\n市面上大把 PGDE 甚至 master <br />\n就算 TA 0.幾 CM GM 照狗衝<br />\n供過於求就係咁啦<br />\n要怪就怪政府一直無視依個問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"教師，醫護學位畢到業就發牌係事實，自然多人中途出家，好正常，一畢業有牌就係已經算係專業<br />\n<br />\n工程畢業大把人因為各種原因畢業後 N 年都 charter 唔到都係事實，嚴格黎講無註册嘅工程師都唔可以叫做註册嘅專業工程師，咁做專業嘅工程師門檻咪相對高囉<br />\n<br />\n一個專科醫生 MBBS 畢業後再專科實習，咁專科醫生嘅專業資格門檻咪再高啲囉<br />\n<br />\n所有政府註册人士，認可人士，專業人士都有自己嘅 code of conduct 去維持自己嘅專業水準，作為 registered teacher 都要對自己嘅專業負責，對自己嘅學生負責<br />\n<br />\n我由頭到尾都係指拎到個專業資格嘅相對難易程度，從來無踐踏任何專業，亦從來無講過 maintain professional ethics 同 integrity 易事，所有專業人士要確切維持自己嘅 professionalism 從來唔係易事，唔好過份演繹"},{"pid":"f842dba57bca1c28dd031213e06bf7609e50eebf","tid":1979182,"uid":26287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb16e8628e534014b523a4f3c75eaac4ff49183","tid":1979182,"uid":304916,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a65a1ff70e2d0d91aa326da5e4bba94be138fad","tid":1979182,"uid":298477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"09b7e568ec62b652cf2c37cae63d3ca01df092bc","tid":1979182,"uid":304916,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"你拎教師同 ACO CA 比，係咪搞笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰衰地 GM 都 degree 職系<br />\nACO CA 只係中四五<br />\n<br />\n我指入行比起其他專業門檻低<br />\nPGDE 你肯俾錢去讀<br />\n讀完就有教師資格<br />\n有資格唔等於有教席<br />\n市面上大把 PGDE 甚至 master <br />\n就算 TA 0.幾 CM GM 照狗衝<br />\n供過於求就係咁啦<br />\n要怪就怪政府一直無視依個問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"教師，醫護